<br>
This is supposed to be the best weapon for bards at the end of OoW.  The 2.0 attainable only by the top guilds (during OoW).  Lets put in ideas worthy of that.<br>
<br>
Adding in effects that are not currently in game have a tendency not to appear on other weapons/equipment till years later.  In other words, you'll be tied to your epic.  The SSS was a great item, but (other than kunark era) is a crappy weapon.  The epic 2.0 will eventually be collecting dust in the bank.  Remeber that when you are designing these things. <p><center>
