<br>
Ratio, of course, should be appropriate and make the first person who finishes the quest take a gasp!<br>
<br>
Stats should, as stated, be beyond anything previously encountered.  Equal to or better than whatever top end OoW gear.  Especially on hps and saves.  Perhaps even new mods that expand beyond the current stat caps.<br>
