<br>
No clickie, proc:  Gift of the Muse/Minstrel/Maestro.  Pick one.  Standard proc rate, 70 percent haste/PoV/wind of marr all combined.  Same duration as DotB.  No stacking but you get a proc with superior haste, resists, and mana/regen.<br>
<br>
Just an idea, I'm open to more and better thoughts.  I'm sure you folks have both!<br>
